    "body": "This could be implemented by analyzing the content of the requested article.\r\n\r\nInput: `/api/law/{statute_name}_{article_number}` (just same as /api/article/:query)\r\nOutput: \r\n```javascript \r\n{\r\n    'isSuccess': boolean // This API call is success or not\r\n    'reason': string // API fail reason. Not exist if isSuccess is true\r\n    'referees': [ // Will not exist if isSuccess is false\r\n        string, // also in format {statute_name}_{article_number}\r\n        string, string, ...\r\n    ]\r\n}\r\n```\r\nElements in the array are strings with the same format as that in `/api/article/:query`. Therefore they can be requested for their contents by API article.\r\n\r\nFor example:\r\nInput: `/api/law/民事訴訟法_624-3`\r\nOutput:\r\n```javascript\r\n{\r\n    'isSuccess': true,\r\n    'referees': [\r\n        \"民法_14\"\r\n    ]\r\n}\r\n```"
  },
